_sText: **NOBLOCK REQUIRED** A simple map I made the other day. CT guards the targets whilst T shoots the CT or the targets. Ts start with shotguns+ammo, CT have free awps/p90 + buyzone. Each target is connected to the CTs floor next to it, if all the floors are destroyed then CT are left exposed with no where to hide and get owned. Mass speed = oorange error, I know, but it is harmless. +no fall damage and unprotected map. Shouts to all the members at solidsurf.info, particulary to Jack for publicizing my map.
